en_634229_0	In response to a request made by Mayor of Haputale at Municipal Council, Commander, Security Forces - Central (SF-Cen), Major General Rukmal Dias instructed 1 Officer and 20 Other Ranks of the Security Forces Headquarters - Central (SFHQ-Cen) to contribute to a mega Self-Help (Shramadana) campaign conducted in and around Haputale city, on Thursday (6).
en_634229_1	With the participation of government sector and non-government sector workers and volunteers, the drive went on till evening.
en_634229_2	Mayor, councillors and students in the area too took part in the arrangement.
en_634229_3	The Army was thanked for its cooperation by the Municipal authorities for its active support.
